OL,3,CYouth violence in Birmingham will rise
OL,4,Cif cuts continue, community leader
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe sessions run by Zaf involve all
OL,8,Fdifferent kinds of sports, including
OL,9,Fmartial arts like Muay Thai.
OL,11,FHe began working with youngsters after
OL,12,Fthe murder of his brother-in-law,
OL,13,FSarfraz Khan, who was stabbed to death
OL,14,Fin Sparkbrook.
OL,16,FHis efforts have seen him crowed the
OL,17,Fwinner of the Pride of Birmingham
OL,18,Fawards.
