OL,3,CYouth violence in Birmingham will rise
OL,4,Cif cuts continue, community leader
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FZaf also relies on mentors like Ameer
OL,8,FKhan, who spent seven years behind
OL,9,Fbars and now speaks to young people
OL,10,Fabout his experience, warning them not
OL,11,Fto glamorise prison life.
OL,13,FHe said: "It was a struggle. It was
OL,14,Fnot easy. People think 'oh yeah they
OL,15,Fget a trophy for going to prison and
OL,16,Fstuff like that'.
OL,18,F"I was sad, I was ashamed. I wished I
OL,19,Fnever was there.
