OL,3,CYouth violence in Birmingham will rise
OL,4,Cif cuts continue, community leader
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Don't look at that guy who's got a
OL,8,Ffancy car driving around your local
OL,9,Fblock up to no good.
OL,11,F"Look at that doctor, that guy who's
OL,12,Fstudied at university and become a
OL,13,Fdoctor or that accountant or that
OL,14,Flawyer or maybe that footballer. Try
OL,15,Fto follow them."
OL,17,FZaf was recently made Chair of
OL,18,FCrimestoppers' West Midlands Volunteer
OL,19,FCommittee.
