OL,4,Cif cuts continue, community leader
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"It might not necessarily be that they
OL,8,Fdon't want to talk to the police. It
OL,9,Fmight be that there's a gang who
OL,10,Fpotentially be saying 'we could be
OL,11,Fdoing damage to yourself or your
OL,12,Ffamily.
OL,14,F"So we just offer that option where
OL,15,Fthey can come and report the crime to
OL,16,Fus and they can remain completely
OL,17,Fanonymous."
